<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Disrobe" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Disrobe,</orth> to divest, to strip: <cit><quote>d. the images,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jc 1.1.69" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. I, 1, 69</bibl></cit>. With <emph>of</emph>: <cit><quote>d. the lion of that robe,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jn 2.142" default="NO" valid="yes">John II, 142</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I'll d. me of these Italian weeds,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 5.1.22" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 1, 22</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>